{"id":25732,"date":"2023-09-28T09:06:09","date_gmt":"2023-09-28T07:06:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?p=25732"},"modified":"2023-09-28T09:07:19","modified_gmt":"2023-09-28T07:07:19","slug":"heidelberg-materials-enters-into-a-strategic-cooperation-with-svedin","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/en\/assignment\/heidelberg-materials-enters-into-a-strategic-cooperation-with-svedin\/","title":{"rendered":"Heidelberg Materials enters into a strategic cooperation with Svedin"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">Heidelberg Materials Betong Sverige AB (\u201d<strong>Heidelberg<\/strong>\u201d) has on 21 June 2023 entered into a shareholders\u2019 agreement with Svedin Holding AB (\u201d<strong>Svedin<\/strong>\u201d) regarding their joint ownership of the newly formed Construction Logistics Sweden AB (\u201d<strong>CLS<\/strong>\u201d). Closing of the transaction took place on 25 September 2023.<\/p>\n<p>CLS shall provide transport and logistic services to the Heidelberg group. Heidelberg owns 49% of CLS and Svedin owns 51% of CLS. Heidelberg and Svedin have, either by themselves or through their subsidiaries, transferred certain assets\/employees to CLS and shall provide certain services to CLS. The strategic cooperation is an important part of the Heidelberg group\u2019s de-carbonization roadmap project.<\/p>\n<p>Heidelberg was advised by Mannheimer Swartling in the transaction.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Heidelberg Materials Betong Sverige AB (\u201dHeidelberg\u201d) has on 21 June 2023 entered into a shareholders\u2019 agreement with Svedin Holding AB (\u201dSvedin\u201d) regarding their joint ownership\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":16,"featured_media":25729,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4313],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-25